This project was inspired by and builds upon ideas from the following projects:

- groundwork (https://github.com/etr/groundwork/)
  AI-native development toolkit with skill-based architecture.

- superpowers (https://github.com/obra/superpowers/)
  Claude Code skill framework for structured development workflows
  including brainstorming, planning, and execution patterns.

- claude-plugins-official (https://github.com/anthropics/claude-plugins-official/)
  Official Claude Code plugin examples and skill definitions from Anthropic.

We are grateful to the authors and contributors of these projects for
their work and for making it available to the community.
